'''橫斑林鴞'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Strix varia''）是[[鴟鴞科|鴟鴞科]][[林鴞屬|林鴞屬]]的一種大型[[貓頭鷹|貓頭鷹]]。

==特徵==
[[File:Barred_Owl.jpg|thumb]]。]]
橫斑林鴞長44-46厘米，翼展101-115厘米。它們的面部淡色，[[眼睛|眼睛]]周圍有深色的環。喙呈黃色，眼睛褐色。它們是[[美國|美國]]東部唯一擁有褐色的眼睛的[[貓頭鷹|貓頭鷹]]，其他的都是黃色眼睛。[[頭部|頭部]]很圓，沒有耳羽。上身呈灰褐色，下身為淺色且有斑紋。[[胸部|胸部]]有白色橫斑。腳上長有[[羽毛|羽毛]]。<ref name="Terres">{{cite book|last=Terres|first=J. K.|title=The Audubon Society Encyclopedia of North American Birds|url=https://archive.org/details/audubonsocietyen00terr|publisher=Knopf|date=1980|location=New York, NY|pages=[https://archive.org/details/audubonsocietyen00terr/page/665 665]|isbn=0394466519}}</ref>

==分佈及棲息地==
橫斑林鴞分佈在[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[美國|美國]]東部及[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的密林中[[繁殖|繁殖]]<ref name = iucn/>，近年擴展至美國西部，具备领地意识。研究顯示[[郊區|郊區]]很適合它們棲息，它們在郊區的數量比在[[古老原始林|古老原始林]]的上升更快。它們在郊區的威脅只有[[車輛|車輛]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.livescience.com/animals/071017-urban-owls.html|title=Owls Get Wise to Better Life in Cities|author=Jeanna Bryner|date=2007-10-17|publisher=LiveScience|accessdate=2011-01-21|archive-date=2008-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081011132440/http://www.livescience.com/animals/071017-urban-owls.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==與北方斑點鴞的關係==
[[Image:Barred_owl.jpg|thumb]]的橫斑林鴞。]]
橫斑林鴞對於在[[美國|美國]][[華盛頓州|華盛頓州]]、[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]及[[俄勒岡州|俄勒岡州]]的[[北方斑點鴞|北方斑點鴞]]的衰落須負上部份責任。自1960年代，橫斑林鴞就向西擴展。<ref>{{Cite web|author=Scott Gremel|year=2000|url=http://www2.nature.nps.gov/YearInReview/yir2000/pages/02_nps_science/02_03_gremel.html|title=Barred Owl Displaces Northern Spotted Owl at Olympic|work=Natural Resources Year in Review|publisher=National Park System|accessdate=2011-01-21|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110613203450/http://www.nature.nps.gov/YearInReview/yir2000/pages/02_nps_science/02_03_gremel.html|archivedate=2011-06-13}}</ref>當北方斑點鴞與橫斑林鴞在同一環境下，後者一般會具有攻擊性，令前者的數量減少。<ref>{{Cite journal|url=http://www.specifysoftware.org/Informatics/bios/biostownpeterson/PR_CB_2003.pdf|title=Using Ecological-Niche Modeling to Predict Barred Owl Invasions with Implications for Spotted Owl Conservation|author=A. Townsend Peterson and C. Richard Robins|journal=Conservation Biology|pages=1161-5|volume=17|issue=4|year=2003|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080627040936/http://www.specifysoftware.org/Informatics/bios/biostownpeterson/PR_CB_2003.pdf|archivedate=2008-06-27}}</ref>這兩種[[貓頭鷹|貓頭鷹]]也會[[混種|混種]]。

==行為及生態==
===繁殖===
橫斑林鴞一般會在樹穴築巢，也會佔用[[烏鴉|烏鴉]]及[[松鼠|松鼠]]的巢。<ref>{{cite book|last=Sattler|first=Helen Roney|title=The Book of North American Owls|publisher=Clarion Books|date=1995|pages=41|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=0r9zfdUYNA0C&pg=PA41&dq=Strix+varia&as_brr=3&client=firefox-a&sig=ACfU3U1bq5hOUJ7fVJNmf0bL2Amb5nH4iA|isbn=0395605245}}</ref>它們是[[留鳥|留鳥]]，但在[[繁殖|繁殖]]季節後也會離開。當位點適合築巢，它們往往會重用此地方。在[[美國|美國]][[佛羅里達州|佛羅里達州]]南部的會在1月初生蛋，而在[[緬因州|緬因州]]北部的則會在4月中生蛋，每次生2-4隻蛋。雌鳥會負責孵蛋，孵化約需4星期。雛鳥要4-5個星期大才會換羽。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.smm.org/warnernaturecenter/animals/owl/|title=Barred Owl Factsheet|author=Lee and Rose Warner Nature Center|year=2008|access-date=2011-01-21|archive-date=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428114551/http://www.smm.org/warnernaturecenter/animals/owl|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===食性===
橫斑林鴞主要吃[[小鼠屬|小鼠屬]]的多個[[物種|物種]]，也會吃細小的[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]及[[鳥類|鳥類]]（如[[松雞科|松雞科]]、[[鳩鴿科|鳩鴿科]]及[[鴨|鴨]]）。它們有時會涉水捕[[魚|魚]]或[[龜鱉類|龜鱉類]]。<ref name="Terres"/><ref>[http://www.owling.com/Barred_nh.htm Barred Owl] {{Wayback|url=http://www.owling.com/Barred_nh.htm |date=20161025095125 }}, Owling</ref><ref name=USFWS>[http://www.nwrc.usgs.gov/wdb/pub/hsi/hsi-143.pdf Habitat Suitability Index Models:Barred Owl] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nwrc.usgs.gov/wdb/pub/hsi/hsi-143.pdf |date=20190531040430 }}, US Fish and Wildlife Service</ref>

橫斑林鴞會在夜間獵食，停留在高處等候獵物，或是在林間飛行搜尋獵物。它們是[[北美洲|北美洲]]中在日間最活躍的[[貓頭鷹|貓頭鷹]]，尤其是在哺育雛鳥。<ref name="Terres"/><ref name=USFWS/>

